== 接受度 ==
交响乐团应用一经发布就收到了非常积极的评论，Shane Richmond在电讯报的一则5星级评论中描述该应用为“内容丰富，还有助睡眠”，后来继续称道，“凭借交响乐团，Touch Press制作出了可能是它的第一个不能以任何其他形式存在的应用”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Richmond|first1=Shane|title=iPad app: The Orchestra review|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/mobile-app-reviews/9725833/iPad-app-The-Orchestra-review.html|accessdate=17 December 2014|work=The Telegraph|date=6 December 2012|archive-date=2017-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702023641/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/mobile-app-reviews/9725833/iPad-app-The-Orchestra-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Slate称交响乐团为“一个完全令人惊叹的新应用”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Walls|first1=Seth Colter|title=The Perfect Classical Music App|url=http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/culturebox/2012/12/the_orchestra_the_best_classical_music_ipad_app_from_esa_pekka_salonen.html|accessdate=17 December 2014|work=Slate|date=21 December 2012|archive-date=2014-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217091238/http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/culturebox/2012/12/the_orchestra_the_best_classical_music_ipad_app_from_esa_pekka_salonen.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而卫报则描述为，“迷人的身临其境般的体验，创造出......古典音乐领域互动性的新东西”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Service|first1=Tom|title=The Orchestra: a new iPad app that strikes all the right notes|url=http://www.theguardian.com/music/tomserviceblog/2012/dec/07/the-orchestra-ipad-app-philharmonia|accessdate=17 December 2014|work=The Guardian|date=7 December 2012|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111191133/http://www.theguardian.com/music/tomserviceblog/2012/dec/07/the-orchestra-ipad-app-philharmonia|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

